{"tid":572500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與龔嘉欣飛沖繩自駕遊 姚子羚兩度遭警察截停","createTime":"2018-02-25T15:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T07:35:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1169daedbe169717d7e623a4cd3fe148df6e814c","tid":572500,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180225/s00007/06ed69e2af7388eaf9703764978cd40c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180225%2Fs00007%2F06ed69e2af7388eaf9703764978cd40c.jpg&h=806cda95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【今日直擊】姚子羚今日孖好姊妹黃智雯及姚子羚出席商場賀年活動，以樽領裙示人，大玩密實。姚子羚透露新年期間跟胡定欣、陳山聰及胡諾言等拜年兼開賭局，結果胡定欣輸了3000元，成為當日大輸家。<br />\n<br />\n提到早前與龔嘉欣飛沖繩自駕遊，姚子羚指難得有3日農曆新年假期，於是出埠去賞櫻花，可惜因不熟悉當地交通規則，兩度遭警察截停，幸未有收到告票。被指刻意撇下男友，姚子羚說：「他不在香港我才約嘉欣去旅行，難得大家都有空，兩個女仔乘機談心事。」"},{"pid":"051e42ab75a6ce1478fcd66cf6d5187a6f2a4214","tid":572500,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會磨豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279276f056d4a411e394253bd5c169a100823d1c","tid":572500,"uid":75692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"好想玩3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0415af0ad07fd86bd1153771a1ba97a76e4eb87d","tid":572500,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279276f056d4a411e394253bd5c169a100823d1c","tid":572500,"uid":75692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"好想玩3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"見兩個靚女<br />\n<br />\n截一截先  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0fdaa282a550fa91c73484b2827bc4fc991f56","tid":572500,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"051e42ab75a6ce1478fcd66cf6d5187a6f2a4